ffect should thus produce a distance bias that increases\nwith redshift and could significantly bias measurements of cosmological\nparameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Aug 2014 20:14:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
