ctive) tensor norm on the\nBanach-space tensor product between the Lipschitz-free space over X and E. In\nterms of the space X^#\\boxast E^*, we describe the spaces of Lipschitz compact\n(finite-rank, approximable) operators from X to E^$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Aug 2014 14:45:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 May 2015 12:15:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-21"}
